<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .toxic-content {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .toxic-words {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Warning: Inappropriate Content Detected</h2>
    
    <div class="warning-box">
        <p>Dear user,</p>
        <p>We have detected inappropriate content in your recent comment. This type of content violates our community guidelines.</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Your Comment:</h3>
    <div class="toxic-content">
        {{ commentContent }}
    </div>

    <h3>Detected Issues:</h3>
    <ul>
        {% for word in toxicWords %}
            <li class="toxic-words">{{ word }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{ reason }}</p>

    <p>Please review our community guidelines and ensure your future comments adhere to our standards. Repeated violations may result in account restrictions.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Your Site Team</p>
</body>
</html> 